" vim-commentary
function UnmapCommentary()
  unmap gc
  nunmap gcc
endfunction
autocmd VimEnter * call UnmapCommentary()
xmap <leader>c  <Plug>Commentary
omap <leader>c  <Plug>Commentary
nmap <leader>cc <Plug>CommentaryLine

